# GIT BASH COMMAND CHEAT SHEET 

![markdown logo](data:image/png;base64,)

## clear

```
Clean terminal
```

## ls 

```
Show elements in directory/route
```

## pwd

```
Show current route
```

## cd

```
travel to initial directory
```

## cd + name

```
travel to target directory
```

## cd ../

```
Go to previous directory
```

## touch + name.txt

```
create target file
```

## rm + name

```
Delete target file
```
## mkdir + name

```
Create target folder
```
## rm - r

```
Delete target directory
```
## code + route

```
Open visual code w/ target route
```
